pick.blurb: Rave Atlas is celebrating 2 years since it's initial conception at its home ground Suicide Circus. Soma Records leaders Slam headline this edition alongside some of the city's most interesting artists who are pushing the boundaries within Techno.
42 hours of high-energy sounds courtesy of Patrick Mason, Herrensauna resident CEM, Radiant Love boss Byron Yeates and many more.

title: DURCH w/ Frederic, Brutalismus3000, hybral, Dance Divine, GIA, Giulia_,Dj Schere & Dj Pheromone

pick.blurb: Queer techno rave DURCH is back. Expect hard and fast sounds including a set from gabber punk duo Brutalismus 3000. The party will be taking donations at the door for women in Afghanistan.

title: Climate 24 hours: Ben UFO, Laurel Halo, DJ Nigga Fox

pick.blurb: Climate of Fear is back for the first time since February 2020 with a huge lineup including Azu Tiwaline, Laurel Halo and DJ Python.
Running for over 24 hours, Terminal V's first international event is a mouthwatering techno marathon featuring Octave One, Paula Temple and many more.
Beloved queer party Herrensauna is back at Revier Südost. Expect things hard, fast and heady with a lineup that includes Jana Rush, Lee Gamble and SPFDJ.

title: 1312 Blank Street - No Future No Past - ://about birthday
Else : Emily Jeanne, Marco Shuttle, Peter Van Hoesen, Refracted, Van Anh

pick.blurb: A marathon party at ://about blank spanning house, techno, trance, breaks and everything in between. Highlights on the bill include Adam Pits & Lisene, DJ Fingerblast and ERIS.

Whether it's the jewel in your calendar or your third party of the weekend, don't miss The MUDD Show's big Easter bonanza with Vera, Tho and plenty more wicked DJs. It's likely to be the talk of the town come Monday.
